Package tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Viewmodel.GameLogicHandlers

Class BuildModeHandler

java.lang.Object
tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Viewmodel.GameLogicHandlers.BuildModeHandler
public class BuildModeHandler
extends java.lang.Object
BuildModeHandler computes the operations related to the building mode such as creating obstacle instances and setting their locations
Author:
Can Usluel
